<p>Wednesday 7 November</p>
<p>Fine &amp; Sunny but the roads are dangerous.<br/>Trip to A.D.M.S. Office at Scottish Lines Busseboom &amp; 15th Field Ambulance.<br/>To 5th D.S.C. Workshops for another saddle spring.<br/>Booked seats in Poperinghe for some of the boys &ndash; at the "Duds" Show.  This reminds one of a 1st Class performance in London.  Everything was perfect last night when we were there, and the Hall was packed<br/>Met Norman Broadbent<br/>Cards and writing after tea.</p>
